const Q_HAUSA_2011=[{"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>1", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"><strong>I</strong> <br/> A wani gari can yamma da Magumi, wai shi Tsauni, an yi wani yaro mai suna Salihi. Iyayensa ba masu wadata ba ne, amma sun yi kokarin ganin ya yi ilmin boko dana Arabiya. Bayan Salihi ya kammala karatun firamare, sai mahaifinsa Tanimu, ya nema masa makarantar gaba da firamare. Domin an ce \"Ilimi gishirin zaman duniya.\" <br/> Amma kuma samo wa Salihi babbar makarantar Magumi bai yi wa mahaifiyarsa Dahira dadi ba, don bata son danta ya yi nesa da ita. Dalili shi ne dansu tilo namiji, sauran hudun kuwa duk mata ne. Bugu da kari, tana jin munanan labarai iri-iri da kan faru a irin wadannan makarantu.  <br/>   <br/> Bayan Salihi ya isa makaranta, sai ya dukufa kan karatu gadan-gadan. Zuwansa ke da wuya, sai suka kulla abota da wani dan ajinsu, wai shi Kasa. Kafin ya ankara, sai da abokinsa ya jefa shi cikin wata kungiyar asiri.  <br/>  <br/>  <br/> Da ya farga da halin da ya shiga, sai ya yi kokarin fita daga cikinta, amma aka nuna masa ai ba a haka. \"In har ka ce za ka fice, lallai za a kassara ka, ko ma a halaka ka\" in ji abokinsa.  <br/>  <br/> Ganin halin tsaka-mai-wuya da ya shiga, sai ya tsayar da shawarar ya fallasa kungiyar, in ya so komai ta tafasa to kone. Ya je ya shaida wa shugaban makaranta.  Nan take ya sanya jami'an tsaro suka kamo dukkan 'yan kungiyar. Kotu ta yanke musu hukunci, sannan aka kai su gidan jarun. Da ma an ce, \"Komai nisan jifa kasa za ya fado.\" <br/>  <br/> Mece ce dangantakar Salihi da Dahira?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Wa da kanwa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Uba da 'ya</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Miji da mata</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Da da Uwa</div>"], "answer": 3, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Dangantakar Salihi da Dahira ita ce dangantakar 'Da da Uwa'. Salihi shi ne 'dan' (wato yaro), Dahira kuwa ita ce 'uwa' (wato mahaifiya). Haka nan, dangantakar Salihi da Dahira ita ce dangantakar 'Da da Uwa'.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>2", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> <strong>I</strong> <br/> A wani gari can yamma da Magumi, wai shi Tsauni, an yi wani yaro mai suna Salihi. Iyayensa ba masu wadata ba ne, amma sun yi kokarin ganin ya yi ilmin boko dana Arabiya. Bayan Salihi ya kammala karatun firamare, sai mahaifinsa Tanimu, ya nema masa makarantar gaba da firamare. Domin an ce \"Ilimi gishirin zaman duniya.\" <br/> Amma kuma samo wa Salihi babbar makarantar Magumi bai yi wa mahaifiyarsa Dahira dadi ba, don bata son danta ya yi nesa da ita. Dalili shi ne dansu tilo namiji, sauran hudun kuwa duk mata ne. Bugu da kari, tana jin munanan labarai iri-iri da kan faru a irin wadannan makarantu.  <br/>   <br/> Bayan Salihi ya isa makaranta, sai ya dukufa kan karatu gadan-gadan. Zuwansa ke da wuya, sai suka kulla abota da wani dan ajinsu, wai shi Kasa. Kafin ya ankara, sai da abokinsa ya jefa shi cikin wata kungiyar asiri.  <br/>  <br/>  <br/> Da ya farga da halin da ya shiga, sai ya yi kokarin fita daga cikinta, amma aka nuna masa ai ba a haka. \"In har ka ce za ka fice, lallai za a kassara ka, ko ma a halaka ka\" in ji abokinsa.  <br/>  <br/> Ganin halin tsaka-mai-wuya da ya shiga, sai ya tsayar da shawarar ya fallasa kungiyar, in ya so komai ta tafasa to kone. Ya je ya shaida wa shugaban makaranta.  Nan take ya sanya jami'an tsaro suka kamo dukkan 'yan kungiyar. Kotu ta yanke musu hukunci, sannan aka kai su gidan jarun. Da ma an ce, \"Komai nisan jifa kasa za ya fado.\" <br/> Wane take ya fi dacewa da wannan labari?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Ilimi gishirin zaman duniya.'</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Ramin karya kurarrw ne.'</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Alheri danko ne...'</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Ba a fafar gora...'</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The story revolves around Salihi who was led into a secret society by his friend Kasa. The society threatened him with death if he tried to leave. However, Salihi decided to expose the society to the school principal, leading to the arrest of all members of the society. The court passed judgement on them and they were taken to prison. The saying 'Ramin karya kurarrw ne.' which translates to 'The end of deceit is disgrace.' best fits the story as it describes the outcome of the secret society's deceitful actions.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>3", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> <strong>I</strong> <br/> A wani gari can yamma da Magumi, wai shi Tsauni, an yi wani yaro mai suna Salihi. Iyayensa ba masu wadata ba ne, amma sun yi kokarin ganin ya yi ilmin boko dana Arabiya. Bayan Salihi ya kammala karatun firamare, sai mahaifinsa Tanimu, ya nema masa makarantar gaba da firamare. Domin an ce \"Ilimi gishirin zaman duniya.\" <br/> Amma kuma samo wa Salihi babbar makarantar Magumi bai yi wa mahaifiyarsa Dahira dadi ba, don bata son danta ya yi nesa da ita. Dalili shi ne dansu tilo namiji, sauran hudun kuwa duk mata ne. Bugu da kari, tana jin munanan labarai iri-iri da kan faru a irin wadannan makarantu.  <br/>   <br/> Bayan Salihi ya isa makaranta, sai ya dukufa kan karatu gadan-gadan. Zuwansa ke da wuya, sai suka kulla abota da wani dan ajinsu, wai shi Kasa. Kafin ya ankara, sai da abokinsa ya jefa shi cikin wata kungiyar asiri.  <br/>  <br/>  <br/> Da ya farga da halin da ya shiga, sai ya yi kokarin fita daga cikinta, amma aka nuna masa ai ba a haka. \"In har ka ce za ka fice, lallai za a kassara ka, ko ma a halaka ka\" in ji abokinsa.  <br/>  <br/> Ganin halin tsaka-mai-wuya da ya shiga, sai ya tsayar da shawarar ya fallasa kungiyar, in ya so komai ta tafasa to kone. Ya je ya shaida wa shugaban makaranta.  Nan take ya sanya jami'an tsaro suka kamo dukkan 'yan kungiyar. Kotu ta yanke musu hukunci, sannan aka kai su gidan jarun. Da ma an ce, \"Komai nisan jifa kasa za ya fado.\" <br/> Wane ne ya shigar da Salihi cikin kungiyar asiri?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Dahiru </div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Monitansu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kasa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Malaminsu</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">From the story, it was Salihi's friend Kasa who introduced him into the secret society. Therefore, the correct answer is Kasa.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>4", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> <strong>I</strong> <br/> A wani gari can yamma da Magumi, wai shi Tsauni, an yi wani yaro mai suna Salihi. Iyayensa ba masu wadata ba ne, amma sun yi kokarin ganin ya yi ilmin boko dana Arabiya. Bayan Salihi ya kammala karatun firamare, sai mahaifinsa Tanimu, ya nema masa makarantar gaba da firamare. Domin an ce \"Ilimi gishirin zaman duniya.\" <br/> Amma kuma samo wa Salihi babbar makarantar Magumi bai yi wa mahaifiyarsa Dahira dadi ba, don bata son danta ya yi nesa da ita. Dalili shi ne dansu tilo namiji, sauran hudun kuwa duk mata ne. Bugu da kari, tana jin munanan labarai iri-iri da kan faru a irin wadannan makarantu.  <br/>   <br/> Bayan Salihi ya isa makaranta, sai ya dukufa kan karatu gadan-gadan. Zuwansa ke da wuya, sai suka kulla abota da wani dan ajinsu, wai shi Kasa. Kafin ya ankara, sai da abokinsa ya jefa shi cikin wata kungiyar asiri.  <br/>  <br/>  <br/> Da ya farga da halin da ya shiga, sai ya yi kokarin fita daga cikinta, amma aka nuna masa ai ba a haka. \"In har ka ce za ka fice, lallai za a kassara ka, ko ma a halaka ka\" in ji abokinsa.  <br/>  <br/> Ganin halin tsaka-mai-wuya da ya shiga, sai ya tsayar da shawarar ya fallasa kungiyar, in ya so komai ta tafasa to kone. Ya je ya shaida wa shugaban makaranta.  Nan take ya sanya jami'an tsaro suka kamo dukkan 'yan kungiyar. Kotu ta yanke musu hukunci, sannan aka kai su gidan jarun. Da ma an ce, \"Komai nisan jifa kasa za ya fado.\" <br/> Ina aka kai su Kasa bayan an yanke musu hukunci?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Tsauni</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Yamma da Magumi</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ga shugaban makaranta</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kurkuku</div>"], "answer": 3, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">\"Kotu ta yanke muzu hukucin Zaman jarun\" is correct.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>5", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> <strong>I</strong> <br/> A wani gari can yamma da Magumi, wai shi Tsauni, an yi wani yaro mai suna Salihi. Iyayensa ba masu wadata ba ne, amma sun yi kokarin ganin ya yi ilmin boko dana Arabiya. Bayan Salihi ya kammala karatun firamare, sai mahaifinsa Tanimu, ya nema masa makarantar gaba da firamare. Domin an ce \"Ilimi gishirin zaman duniya.\" <br/> Amma kuma samo wa Salihi babbar makarantar Magumi bai yi wa mahaifiyarsa Dahira dadi ba, don bata son danta ya yi nesa da ita. Dalili shi ne dansu tilo namiji, sauran hudun kuwa duk mata ne. Bugu da kari, tana jin munanan labarai iri-iri da kan faru a irin wadannan makarantu.  <br/>   <br/> Bayan Salihi ya isa makaranta, sai ya dukufa kan karatu gadan-gadan. Zuwansa ke da wuya, sai suka kulla abota da wani dan ajinsu, wai shi Kasa. Kafin ya ankara, sai da abokinsa ya jefa shi cikin wata kungiyar asiri.  <br/>  <br/>  <br/> Da ya farga da halin da ya shiga, sai ya yi kokarin fita daga cikinta, amma aka nuna masa ai ba a haka. \"In har ka ce za ka fice, lallai za a kassara ka, ko ma a halaka ka\" in ji abokinsa.  <br/>  <br/> Ganin halin tsaka-mai-wuya da ya shiga, sai ya tsayar da shawarar ya fallasa kungiyar, in ya so komai ta tafasa to kone. Ya je ya shaida wa shugaban makaranta.  Nan take ya sanya jami'an tsaro suka kamo dukkan 'yan kungiyar. Kotu ta yanke musu hukunci, sannan aka kai su gidan jarun. Da ma an ce, \"Komai nisan jifa kasa za ya fado.\" <br/> Wane ne tauraron labarin?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Mahaifin Salihi</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Salihi.</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kasa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Mahaifiyar Salihi</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The protagonist of the story is Salihi. He is the one who went through the journey of education, joined a secret society, and eventually exposed the society to the school authority. Therefore, he is the hero of the story.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>6", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"><strong>II</strong> <br/> Hausawa wasu mutane ne da suka ba abinci muhimmanci a rayuwarsu, domin duk wata fafitika da gwama numfashi da ba hammata iska, ana yi wa ciki ne. Wato cikin biyu: daya ya yiwu an ci an koshi, ko kuma ana cikin halin nema ne.  <br/>  <br/> Kullum, da zaran gari ya waye, wasu tun da jijjifi, za a ga sun fita neman abin da za su ci, su da iyalansu, domin a samu rufin asiri. Saboda  haka, ba a barin kowa a gida sai tsofaffi da mata da yara da kuma ragwage, kowa ya tafi neman halaliya.  <br/>  <br/>  A al'adance, hausawa suna da lokuta uku na cin abinci a kowaca rana, wato safe da rana da dare. A mafi yawan lokuta da safe akan sha abu mai ruwa-ruwa, kamar koko da kosai ko kunu. Wasu kuma, sukan dumama abin da aka ci a daren da ya gabata. Da rana, kuma akan dafa duk irin abin da ya samu kamar shinkafa da wake ko dambu ko kuma danwake. Da daddare kuma, kusan kowane gida za a sa mu cewa ana dafa tuwo da miya ne, ko miyar kuka ko kubewa ko taushe ko kalkashi da dai sauransu, da nama ko babu nama. Duk ko ma mene ne ya samu, wato dai \"Daidai ruwa daidai kurji.\" <br/>  <br/> Har ila yau, ko da yake ba kowa yake da karfin dora girki sau uku ba a rana saboda halin yau, amma a kan sami makwabta na gari masu tausayi da lura, su kan kira makwabtansu domin su ci abincin, ko suna da shi ko ba su da shi. Da ma tunfil-azal, an san Bahaushe da halin taimako ga dan'uwansa.  <br/>  <br/>  A zamanin da, za a ga Bahaushe yana kokarin ya yi noma domin kada gidansa a zauna da yunwa. Amma yanzu, zamananci ya mayar da tunaninsa ya koma kan kasuwanci ko aikin ofis a maimakon aikin gona saboda lalaci da son jiki. <br/>  <br/> Me ake nufi da gwama nunfashi a labarin?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Rayuwa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ka-ce-na-ce</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">kwazo</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Saki-na-dafe</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">\"Fada\" is correct; it is the right option in this context.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>7", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> <strong>II</strong> <br/> Hausawa wasu mutane ne da suka ba abinci muhimmanci a rayuwarsu, domin duk wata fafitika da gwama numfashi da ba hammata iska, ana yi wa ciki ne. Wato cikin biyu: daya ya yiwu an ci an koshi, ko kuma ana cikin halin nema ne.  <br/>  <br/> Kullum, da zaran gari ya waye, wasu tun da jijjifi, za a ga sun fita neman abin da za su ci, su da iyalansu, domin a samu rufin asiri. Saboda  haka, ba a barin kowa a gida sai tsofaffi da mata da yara da kuma ragwage, kowa ya tafi neman halaliya.  <br/>  <br/>  A al'adance, hausawa suna da lokuta uku na cin abinci a kowaca rana, wato safe da rana da dare. A mafi yawan lokuta da safe akan sha abu mai ruwa-ruwa, kamar koko da kosai ko kunu. Wasu kuma, sukan dumama abin da aka ci a daren da ya gabata. Da rana, kuma akan dafa duk irin abin da ya samu kamar shinkafa da wake ko dambu ko kuma danwake. Da daddare kuma, kusan kowane gida za a sa mu cewa ana dafa tuwo da miya ne, ko miyar kuka ko kubewa ko taushe ko kalkashi da dai sauransu, da nama ko babu nama. Duk ko ma mene ne ya samu, wato dai \"Daidai ruwa daidai kurji.\" <br/>  <br/> Har ila yau, ko da yake ba kowa yake da karfin dora girki sau uku ba a rana saboda halin yau, amma a kan sami makwabta na gari masu tausayi da lura, su kan kira makwabtansu domin su ci abincin, ko suna da shi ko ba su da shi. Da ma tunfil-azal, an san Bahaushe da halin taimako ga dan'uwansa.  <br/>  <br/>  A zamanin da, za a ga Bahaushe yana kokarin ya yi noma domin kada gidansa a zauna da yunwa. Amma yanzu, zamananci ya mayar da tunaninsa ya koma kan kasuwanci ko aikin ofis a maimakon aikin gona saboda lalaci da son jiki. <br/> Wane suna ya fi dacewa da wannan labarin?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Kowa ya daka rawar wani ...'</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Daidai ruwa daidai kurji.'</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Da ruwan ciki ake jan na rijiya.'</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Noma tushen arziki.'</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The phrase 'Daidai ruwa daidai kurji.' is a recurring theme in the story. It is used to describe the balance in the preparation of meals among the Hausa people. The phrase translates to 'the right amount of water and the right amount of flour' in English, which signifies the importance of balance in meal preparation.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>8", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> <strong>II</strong> <br/> Hausawa wasu mutane ne da suka ba abinci muhimmanci a rayuwarsu, domin duk wata fafitika da gwama numfashi da ba hammata iska, ana yi wa ciki ne. Wato cikin biyu: daya ya yiwu an ci an koshi, ko kuma ana cikin halin nema ne.  <br/>  <br/> Kullum, da zaran gari ya waye, wasu tun da jijjifi, za a ga sun fita neman abin da za su ci, su da iyalansu, domin a samu rufin asiri. Saboda  haka, ba a barin kowa a gida sai tsofaffi da mata da yara da kuma ragwage, kowa ya tafi neman halaliya.  <br/>  <br/>  A al'adance, hausawa suna da lokuta uku na cin abinci a kowaca rana, wato safe da rana da dare. A mafi yawan lokuta da safe akan sha abu mai ruwa-ruwa, kamar koko da kosai ko kunu. Wasu kuma, sukan dumama abin da aka ci a daren da ya gabata. Da rana, kuma akan dafa duk irin abin da ya samu kamar shinkafa da wake ko dambu ko kuma danwake. Da daddare kuma, kusan kowane gida za a sa mu cewa ana dafa tuwo da miya ne, ko miyar kuka ko kubewa ko taushe ko kalkashi da dai sauransu, da nama ko babu nama. Duk ko ma mene ne ya samu, wato dai \"Daidai ruwa daidai kurji.\" <br/>  <br/> Har ila yau, ko da yake ba kowa yake da karfin dora girki sau uku ba a rana saboda halin yau, amma a kan sami makwabta na gari masu tausayi da lura, su kan kira makwabtansu domin su ci abincin, ko suna da shi ko ba su da shi. Da ma tunfil-azal, an san Bahaushe da halin taimako ga dan'uwansa.  <br/>  <br/>  A zamanin da, za a ga Bahaushe yana kokarin ya yi noma domin kada gidansa a zauna da yunwa. Amma yanzu, zamananci ya mayar da tunaninsa ya koma kan kasuwanci ko aikin ofis a maimakon aikin gona saboda lalaci da son jiki. <br/> A labarin an nuna baya ga shan abu mai ruwa-ruwa da safe, wasu Hausawa kan</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">yi tuwo</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">dafa shinkafa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">yi dumame</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">turara dambu</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The question is asking what some Hausa people do after not drinking liquid food in the morning. From the passage, it is stated that 'Wasu kuma, sukan dumama abin da aka ci a daren da ya gabata.' which translates to 'Some, however, repeat what was eaten the previous night.' Therefore, the correct answer is 'yi dumame' which translates to 'repeat'.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>9", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> <strong>II</strong> <br/> Hausawa wasu mutane ne da suka ba abinci muhimmanci a rayuwarsu, domin duk wata fafitika da gwama numfashi da ba hammata iska, ana yi wa ciki ne. Wato cikin biyu: daya ya yiwu an ci an koshi, ko kuma ana cikin halin nema ne.  <br/>  <br/> Kullum, da zaran gari ya waye, wasu tun da jijjifi, za a ga sun fita neman abin da za su ci, su da iyalansu, domin a samu rufin asiri. Saboda  haka, ba a barin kowa a gida sai tsofaffi da mata da yara da kuma ragwage, kowa ya tafi neman halaliya.  <br/>  <br/>  A al'adance, hausawa suna da lokuta uku na cin abinci a kowaca rana, wato safe da rana da dare. A mafi yawan lokuta da safe akan sha abu mai ruwa-ruwa, kamar koko da kosai ko kunu. Wasu kuma, sukan dumama abin da aka ci a daren da ya gabata. Da rana, kuma akan dafa duk irin abin da ya samu kamar shinkafa da wake ko dambu ko kuma danwake. Da daddare kuma, kusan kowane gida za a sa mu cewa ana dafa tuwo da miya ne, ko miyar kuka ko kubewa ko taushe ko kalkashi da dai sauransu, da nama ko babu nama. Duk ko ma mene ne ya samu, wato dai \"Daidai ruwa daidai kurji.\" <br/>  <br/> Har ila yau, ko da yake ba kowa yake da karfin dora girki sau uku ba a rana saboda halin yau, amma a kan sami makwabta na gari masu tausayi da lura, su kan kira makwabtansu domin su ci abincin, ko suna da shi ko ba su da shi. Da ma tunfil-azal, an san Bahaushe da halin taimako ga dan'uwansa.  <br/>  <br/>  A zamanin da, za a ga Bahaushe yana kokarin ya yi noma domin kada gidansa a zauna da yunwa. Amma yanzu, zamananci ya mayar da tunaninsa ya koma kan kasuwanci ko aikin ofis a maimakon aikin gona saboda lalaci da son jiki. <br/> A labarin, akan yi dan wake da </div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">safe</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">rana</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">almuru</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">asuba</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The question is asking when 'dan wake' is prepared. From the passage, it is stated that 'Da rana, kuma akan dafa duk irin abin da ya samu kamar shinkafa da wake ko dambu ko kuma danwake.' which translates to 'In the afternoon, all kinds of food that is available like rice, beans, meat or danwake are cooked.' Therefore, the correct answer is 'rana' which translates to 'afternoon'.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>10", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> <strong>II</strong> <br/> Hausawa wasu mutane ne da suka ba abinci muhimmanci a rayuwarsu, domin duk wata fafitika da gwama numfashi da ba hammata iska, ana yi wa ciki ne. Wato cikin biyu: daya ya yiwu an ci an koshi, ko kuma ana cikin halin nema ne.  <br/>  <br/> Kullum, da zaran gari ya waye, wasu tun da jijjifi, za a ga sun fita neman abin da za su ci, su da iyalansu, domin a samu rufin asiri. Saboda  haka, ba a barin kowa a gida sai tsofaffi da mata da yara da kuma ragwage, kowa ya tafi neman halaliya.  <br/>  <br/>  A al'adance, hausawa suna da lokuta uku na cin abinci a kowaca rana, wato safe da rana da dare. A mafi yawan lokuta da safe akan sha abu mai ruwa-ruwa, kamar koko da kosai ko kunu. Wasu kuma, sukan dumama abin da aka ci a daren da ya gabata. Da rana, kuma akan dafa duk irin abin da ya samu kamar shinkafa da wake ko dambu ko kuma danwake. Da daddare kuma, kusan kowane gida za a sa mu cewa ana dafa tuwo da miya ne, ko miyar kuka ko kubewa ko taushe ko kalkashi da dai sauransu, da nama ko babu nama. Duk ko ma mene ne ya samu, wato dai \"Daidai ruwa daidai kurji.\" <br/>  <br/> Har ila yau, ko da yake ba kowa yake da karfin dora girki sau uku ba a rana saboda halin yau, amma a kan sami makwabta na gari masu tausayi da lura, su kan kira makwabtansu domin su ci abincin, ko suna da shi ko ba su da shi. Da ma tunfil-azal, an san Bahaushe da halin taimako ga dan'uwansa.  <br/>  <br/>  A zamanin da, za a ga Bahaushe yana kokarin ya yi noma domin kada gidansa a zauna da yunwa. Amma yanzu, zamananci ya mayar da tunaninsa ya koma kan kasuwanci ko aikin ofis a maimakon aikin gona saboda lalaci da son jiki. <br/> Labarin ya na nuna cewa Bahuashe yakan yi noma domin</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">neman kudi</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">wadatar zuci</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">karin aure</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">guje wa yunwa</div>"], "answer": 3, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The question is asking why the Hausa man farms. From the passage, it is stated that 'A zamanin da, za a ga Bahaushe yana kokarin ya yi noma domin kada gidansa a zauna da yunwa.' which translates to 'In those days, you would see a Hausa man trying to farm so that his household would not be hungry.' Therefore, the correct answer is 'guje wa yunwa' which translates to 'avoid hunger'.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>11", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">HARSHE: NAHAWU <br/>  <br/> Wannan alamar (-), ita aka fi sani da </div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">wakafi</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">ruwa biyu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">karan dori</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">debewa</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ana amfani da karan-dori wajen hoda kalmomi biyu, domni su ba da ma'ana.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): KÂ’IDOJIN RUBUTU (ORTHOGRAPHY)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>12", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> HARSHE: NAHAWU <br/> Wanne ne kebabben bayanin wasalin /a/?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Dan gaba ne na sama</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Dan gaba ne na tsakiya</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Dan kurya ne na sama</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Dan tsakatsaki ne na kasa.</div>"], "answer": 3, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">\"Harshe na tsayawa a tsakiyar bakin dan Adam\" is correct.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): KÂ’IDOJIN RUBUTU (ORTHOGRAPHY)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>13", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> HARSHE: NAHAWU <br/> Wanne ne dan jirge?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">/m/.</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">/t/</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">/l/</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">/sh/</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">In Hausa Nahawu, the symbol /l/ is referred to as 'dan jirge'. This is a way of classifying the sound based on its position and manner of articulation.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): KÂ’IDOJIN RUBUTU (ORTHOGRAPHY)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>14", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> HARSHE: NAHAWU <br/> Wanne ne bare dangane da jinsi?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Cinnaka</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Hankaka</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Buraka</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Gauraka</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">In Hausa language, 'Bare' refers to gender. Therefore, 'Buraka' is the correct answer as it is the term used to describe gender in Hausa language.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): KÂ’IDOJIN RUBUTU (ORTHOGRAPHY)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>15", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> HARSHE: NAHAWU <br/> A kalmar marubuciya, akwai dafi</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">daya</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">biyu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">uku</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">hudu</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">In Hausa language, 'Marubuciya' means 'female writer'. The word 'Marubuciya' has two syllables, hence the correct answer is 'biyu' which means 'two' in Hausa.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): KÂ’IDOJIN RUBUTU (ORTHOGRAPHY)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>16", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> HARSHE: NAHAWU <br/> Lokaci na Yanzu II shi ne mai manunin lokaci</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">-na</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">za</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">-ke</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">-kan</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">\"Saboda ana cikin aikin ba a kare ba\" is correct; the phrase fits.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): GININ JUMLA (SYNTAX)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>17", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> HARSHE: NAHAWU <br/> Da ya hangi su, ya ce \"Da wa Allah ya hada mu?\" <br/> Wannan na nufin da ya hango su, Sai ya</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">gudu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">bi su a guje</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">boye</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">ja ya tsaya</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The phrase 'Da wa Allah ya hada mu?' translates to 'With whom did God unite us?'. The phrase that follows 'Da ya hango su, Sai ya' translates to 'When he saw them, he...'. The most appropriate completion of this sentence is 'bi su a guje' which means 'ran away in fear'. The other options do not fit the context of the sentence.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>18", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Tambayoyi a kan AL'ADU. <br/>  <br/> Sanya bante ga yara maza a al'adar Bahaushe, na faruwa ne daga.</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Shekara biyu da haihuma </div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">lokacin da yaro ya fara tafiya </div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">shekara uku da haihuwa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">lokachin da aka sha yaro ya warke.</div>"], "answer": 3, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">\"Saboda ya girma\" is correct; it is the correct option.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>19", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan AL'ADU. <br/> Yara masu lakabi cindo an haire su ne</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">da damina</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">lokacin cin doya</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">da yatsu shida</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">ana ruwa</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The question 'Yara masu lakabi cindo an haire su ne' translates to 'Children with the nickname cindo were named during'. The correct answer is 'da yatsu shida' which means 'six months'. This is because in Hausa culture, children are often given nicknames at certain ages or stages of their life, and 'cindo' is a nickname given to a child at six months. The other options do not accurately represent the time at which the nickname 'cindo' is given.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>20", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan AL'ADU. <br/> Dan matar da ke aure a gidan da ba a nan to haife shi ba, shi ne </div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">bora</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">mowa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">agola</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">kado</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Saboda sabin mijin da ta aura ba shi ne ubansa ba.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>21", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan AL'ADU. <br/> Barunje shi ne</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">maharbi</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">malami</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">mahauci</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">masaki</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Mai sayar da nama daidai karamin kusi: abin ban dariya ne.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>22", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan AL'ADU. <br/> Makodi kayan aiki ne na</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">sassaka</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">jima</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">kora</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">wanzanci</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Domin korar kaifin wuka, garam ya fi fortanya d- s.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>23", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan AL'ADU. <br/> Wanne ne biki na sana'a?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Bikin saukar karatu.</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Bikin kamun gwauro</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Bikin kamun kifi</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Bikin kalankuwa</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The question asks for the type of festival that is related to craft. The correct answer is 'Bikin kamun kifi' which translates to 'Fishing festival'. This is because fishing is considered a craft or trade. None of the other options relate to a craft or trade festival.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>24", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan AL'ADU. <br/> Wace hanya ce ake bi domin shiga harkar bori?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Girka</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Garaya</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Addu'a</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Shaushawa</div>"], "answer": 0, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Saboda 'Sulhu' tsakanin aljanu da wanda Suko Shiga jikinsa.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>25", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan AL'ADU. <br/> Wace sarauta ce ta shafi kula da baitulmali?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Sarkin fada</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ma'aji</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Sarkin gida</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Waziri</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The question asks for the title that is responsible for managing the treasury (Baitulmali). The correct answer is 'Ma'aji' which translates to 'Treasurer'. This is because the treasurer is typically responsible for managing funds. The other options do not relate to roles responsible for managing funds.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>26", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan AL'ADU. <br/> A al'adance, wacce hanya ce aka fi amfani da ita wajen magance ciwo?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Tauna</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Turare</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Jiko</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Surace</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Jiko: hanya ce wadda ake bi wajen ammfani da mogani.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>27", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan AL'ADU. <br/> Me furen tumfafiya kan kara wa mutum?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kwarinkashi</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Farin jini</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kwarjini</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Jarumtaka</div>"], "answer": 0, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Saboda yana kara wa mutum kwarjini a wajen mutane.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>28", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Tambayoyi a kan ADABIN BAKA. <br/>  <br/> \"Ja ya fado, ja ya dauka\" <br/> Wane rukunin adabin baka wannan magana ta fito?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Zuben baka</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Maganganun azanci</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Salon magana</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Wakokin baka</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ja ya faɗo, ja ya ɗauka means whoever causes trouble must bear its consequences. It emphasizes that one must face the results of their own actions.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>29", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan ADABIN BAKA. <br/> Labarin kura da akuya da harawa yana cikin nau'in labari na</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">tatsuniya</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">kacici-kacici</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">kissa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">almara</div>"], "answer": 3, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Yaro ya buda tukunya a daji, aljani ya fito, sai ya yaudare shi ya kulle.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>30", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan ADABIN BAKA. <br/> \"Kulun-kulu-fita\"</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Baba</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Gauta</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kanwa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Gishiri</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Kulun-kulu-fita' is a term used to refer to 'Gauta' in Hausa. Gauta is a Hausa term for trumpet. It is a musical instrument that is often used in traditional Hausa music.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>31", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan ADABIN BAKA. <br/> Mece ce dangantakar Gizo da Kki a tatsuniyoyin Hausa?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Wa da kanwa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ubangida da baranya</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Uba da 'ya</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Miji da mata</div>"], "answer": 3, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Matar Gizo mai wayo ce, sunanta Koki a tatsuniyoyi.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>32", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan ADABIN BAKA. <br/> \"Da duniya da gaskiya, da</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">ba a bar huntu a kasuwa ba</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">ba a daure dan sane ba</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">ba a bar mazari tsirara ba</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">an bar zama da kazama</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Iya magana kan ceci kai, amma shirme na jefa cikin hali.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>33", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan ADABIN BAKA. <br/> Wanne ne gaskiya dangane da makadan fada?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ba su yi wa kowa waka sai sarki.</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ba su karbar kyauta sai daga sarki</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Sarkinsu na sa su yi wa wani waka</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Dukkansu makadan taushi ne.</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Idan ya ba su umarnin hakan, dole su bi ba gardama.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>34", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan ADABIN BAKA. <br/> Cikin wadannan, wanne ne ake kadawa?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Jauje </div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Molo</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kwabsa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Garaya</div>"], "answer": 0, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The question asks which of the options is a type of 'kadawa'. In Hausa, 'kadawa' refers to a type of dance. Therefore, the correct answer is 'Jauje' which is a type of dance in Hausa culture.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>35", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> Tambayoyi a kan ADABIN BAKA. <br/> \"Balarabe na Balaraba  <br/> Sannu Balaraba <br/> Sai wata rana.\" <br/>  Me Haruna Uji, ke nuna wa a wannan tsakure?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ambaton Balaraba</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Dangantakarsa da Balaraba.</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ban kwana da duniya</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Yabon Balaraba</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The phrase 'Balarabe na Balaraba, Sannu Balaraba, Sai wata rana' by Haruna Uji, is a form of greeting and shows the relationship between Balarabe and Balaraba. Therefore, the correct answer is 'Dangantakarsa da Balaraba' which means 'His relationship with Balaraba'.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>36", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">RUBUTACCEN ADABI: ZUBE. <br/>  <br/> Jigon labarin \"Kowa Ya Daka Rawar Wani\" na Magana Jari Ce na III na A. na Imam, ya yi daidai da \"Kowa ya </div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ji a Jikinsa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Tsaya Matsayinsa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Ji da Kansa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Shiga Taitayinsa.</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Jigo Lagabim 'kiwa ya daka rawar wani' na magana jari ce na III.  <br/>  Shi ne 'kowa ya tsaya, matsayinsa Saboda a labarin maigisan ya ce Su yi caryi shi da matersa, wati ta se gona shi kuwa ya yi aikin gida, dagakarshe ya gozo koda otumame ya aje mato.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>37", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> RUBUTACCEN ADABI: ZUBE. <br/> Labarun cikin Magana Jari ce na III na A. Imam, an shirya su na bisa salon</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">ji ka karu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">karba - karba</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">koyi da kanka</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">zabi da kanka</div>"], "answer": 0, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Labarin Magana jan ce na III an Shirya su ne bese salan ji ka  <br/>  Karu: Kanar 'Labarin' sai bango ya tsage ka longare kan samu wajen Shiga.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>38", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> RUBUTACCEN ADABI: ZUBE. <br/> labarin 'Kowa Ya Dogara Ga Allah, Kada Ya Ji Tsoron Mahassada, Balle Keta' na cikin Magana Jari Ce na III na A. Imam, ya amsa sunansa ganin yadda</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">aka halaka Waziri</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Sarkin Karaya ya cika umarnin Sarkin Sudan</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">aka yi shagalin sarautar Abdun Ugu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Abdun Ugu ya ketare markicin Waziri</div>"], "answer": 0, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">An halaka Wazirin ne saboda hassada kan Audun Ugu.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>39", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> RUBUTACCEN ADABI: ZUBE. <br/> A Gandoki na Walin Katsina A. Bello an nuna Gandoki ya yi fada har da</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">aljannu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">mata</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">dabbobi</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">sarauniya.</div>"], "answer": 0, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">In the book Gandoki na Walin Katsina by A. Bello, Gandoki is portrayed as a brave warrior who fought even with jinn (supernatural creatures in Islamic mythology). Therefore, the correct answer is option 1: 'aljannu'.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>40", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> RUBUTACCEN ADABI: ZUBE. <br/> 'Ya zama musu alakakai, ko wane juyin suka yi na su halaka shi, shi ke sama, sai ka ce hancin gauta.' <br/> Wane Irin salo aka yi amfani da shi a wannan tsakure na Gandoki na Walin Katsina A. Bello?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Karangiya</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Mutuntarwa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Dabbantawa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kamantawa</div>"], "answer": 3, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">The phrase 'Ya zama musu alakakai, ko wane juyin suka yi na su halaka shi, shi ke sama, sai ka ce hancin gauta.' is an example of Kamantawa, a type of metaphor in Hausa literature where an object or situation is described in a way that it is not in reality but the description helps to create a vivid image in the reader's mind. Therefore, the correct answer is option 4: 'Kamantawa'.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): AUNA FAHIMTA (COMPREHENSION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>41", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">WAKA <br/>  <br/> 'Ya dan'uwa da ke fatawa a kan zancen,  <br/>  Tawakkali da du'al wadda ba bidiá. Da fassarar kaddara bisa yadda anka fadi.  <br/>  Cikin kitabu da sunna wanda ba bidi'a.  <br/>  Ai ka yi fatawarka gun wannan da bai da sani, <br/> Kuma bai da hikima ta rarrabe mas'alar bidi'a.'  <br/>  A wadannan baitoci na 'Wakar Bidi'a ta Wakokin Sa'adu Zungur ana yin gargadi ne kan</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">dacewar mai karatu yayi fatawa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">karancin malamai a yanzu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">fayyace karya cikin gaskiya</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">neman bayani wurin masana</div>"], "answer": 3, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Wato shaharar run malamai na addini ta jawo hassada.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): FASSARA (TRANSLATION)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>42", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> WAKA <br/> Makasudin Wakar 'Yan Baka' ta Sa'adu Zungur shi ne</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">hana hassada</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">hana zunde</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">dakile almubazzaranci</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">dakile jita-jita</div>"], "answer": 3, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kamar yadda mawakin ya fada a baiti na Biyu: Misali.  <br/>  Aboka, tofo nan ko saurari: Waka Jawabi ni yanboko maso zaloka jafo'insu bat sho'ami mayoko  <br/>  Da kaifin halussa awa na moroko  <br/>  Da Daukoko korya bise gaskiya.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>43", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> WAKA <br/> Marubucin 'Wakar Zambon kazama' ta zababbun Wakokin Da Da Na Yanzu na D. Abdulkadir ya nuna cewa mata kazamai suna nuna kazantarsu ta</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">jiki da abinci</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">gida da abinci</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">jiki gida da abinci</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">jiki gida da waje</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kamar yadda ya zo a bauti na 10 zababbun wakokin Da doone yan  <br/>   <br/>  Ran girkinki ba akoshi do jibi, Shi namom miji ki cinye a tsame.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>44", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> WAKA <br/> \"Ita ko bante ta ketara sai ta haihu,  <br/> In ka san kudi su kare a suna\" <br/> Wannan tsakure na 'Wakar Zambon Kazama' ta Nal. Aliyu Namangi, ta Zababbun Wakokin Da Da Na Yanzu, na D. Abdulkadir yana Magana ne, a kan</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">tsofaffi</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">masu gwanne</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">mata karuwai</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">zawarawa</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kamar yadda mowallafin ya rera a baiti na 18 Zababbun Wakokin Da da na Yanzu no D. Abdulkadir na da 'Kwar biyar </div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>45", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> WAKA <br/> Wakar 'Gadar Zare' ta Zababbun Wakokin Da Da na Yanzu na D. Abdulkadir 'yar kwar nawa ce?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Biyu </div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Uku</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Hudu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Biyar</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Shi ne nake sin mu taru mu gane, camfi da kege rashin ilmi ne, Tsafisu bori rashin hankoli ne. Aminci da su ko hakika bata ne, Da wanta da shirme da shorhdiya.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>46", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">WASAN KWAIKWAYO <br/>  <br/> 'Yan wasa mata nawa ne a Kukan Kurciya na M. B. Bambale?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Biyu.</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Uku</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Hudu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Biyar</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">'Yammata yan wasa uku ne  <br/>  1. Binta matar M. Mahmud  <br/>  2. Salamatu ýar M. Mahmud  <br/> 3. Salame Uwargidan M. Sambo.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>47", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> WASAN KWAIKWAYO <br/> 'Wa ya ce ba ni ba! Wa ya yi ni, wa Yai kamata! Wa kuma zai kama bawa fiye da wanda zan kama!'  <br/>   <br/>  Wa ya yi wannan kirari a cikin Shaihu Umar na U. Ladan da D. Lyndersay?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Buhari</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Makau</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kwatau</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Shaihu.</div>"], "answer": 2, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Shaihu Umar na U. Ladan da D. Lyndersay  <br/>  Lokocin do suka kai hari garin gwarawa.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>48", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> WASAN KWAIKWAYO <br/> Rabo nawa wasan Shaihu Umar na U. Ladan da D. Lyndersay ya kunsa?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Biyu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Uku</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Hudu</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Biyar</div>"], "answer": 0, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Rabo Biyu  <br/>  1. Labarin Haihumar Umar, Mutuwar, babansa, aure makau da fatima (wato gyatu matar Umar) makicin Kwatau do sarkin Zagi, washe gisan makaw.  <br/>  2. Rabo na Biyu: Labarin Umar da Abdulkarin da yadda suka fito neman mahaifiyar.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>49", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> WASAN KWAIKWAYO <br/> An tsara Kukan Kurciya na M. B. Bambale</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">fitowa-fitowa da shiga-shiga</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">kashi-kashi da fitowa-fitowa</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">rabo-rabo da kashi-kashi</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">shiga-shiga da rabo-rabo</div>"], "answer": 1, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kukan kuraiya na M. B Bambale ya yi amfani da kashi-kashi da kuma fitowa a wasan.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}, {"id": "objective>Hausa>2011>50", "question": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\"> <br/> WASAN KWAIKWAYO <br/> Su wa Makau ya kira jakkai a wasan Shaihu Umar na U. Ladan Da D. Lyndersay?</div>", "options": ["<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Sarkin Zagi da Wawan Sarki</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kwatau da Wawan Sarki</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Shantali da Kwatau</div>", "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">Kwatau da Sarkin Zagi</div>"], "answer": 3, "explanation": "<div style=\"font-family:Cambria;font-size:17px;\">In the play 'Shaihu Umar' by U. Ladan and D. Lyndersay, Makau called the horses 'Kwatau' and 'Sarkin Zagi'. Therefore, the correct answer is 'Kwatau da Sarkin Zagi'.</div>", "topic": "HARSHE(LANGUAGE): MAÂ’ANA (SEMANTICS)"}];
